**LIX readability score calculator:** https://www.eniro.se/lix-test

**Step 1: Count the number of words (N)**
The text contains 79 words.

**Step 2: Count the number of long words (L)**
A long word is defined as a word with more than 6 letters.

There are 26 long words in the text.

**Step 3: Count the number of sentences (S)**
The text contains 6 sentences.

**Step 4: Calculate LIX**
The LIX formula is LIX = (N + L) / S

LIX = (79 + 26) / 6
LIX = 17.667

**Result:**

LIX=17.667